    • Method Detail

      • start

        void start(java.lang.String instanceName)
        Start the daemon. If this method returns normally (by not throwing an exception), then it is assumed that the daemon has started normally. If this method throws an exception, then it is assumed that the daemon failed to start properly, and the FIFO and pid file will be cleaned up, and the daemon process will exit.
        Parameters:
        instanceName - the instance name for this daemon
